### Instance API Tests
### Tests for InstanceController endpoints
### Uses {{baseUrl}} from http-client.env.json
### Note: instance creation returns 501, so delete requires a manually set instanceId.

### Get all instances
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/instances
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "List instances should return 200");
  client.log("Instances retrieved");
%}

### Create new instance (returns 501 — not implemented by API)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/instances
Content-Type: application/json

> {%
  client.assert(response.status === 501, "Create instance should return 501");
  client.log("Instance creation: not implemented (expected)");
%}
